`
+-------------------+      +-------------------------------------------------+
|     User's        |      |                     DNS                         |
|     Browser       |----->|     (Resolves foobar.com to LB IP 8.8.8.8)    |
+-------------------+      +-------------------------------------------------+
         |                                       |
         | (HTTP/HTTPS Request)                  |
         V                                       V
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                     ** LOAD BALANCER (HAProxy) - IP: 8.8.8.8 **             |
|                  (Distributes traffic to Server 1 & Server 2)               |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
         |                                       | (Round-Robin Distribution)
         |---------------------------------------|
         V                                       V
+---------------------+               +---------------------+
|   ** SERVER 1 **     |               |   ** SERVER 2 **     |
|   (IP: 10.0.0.1)      |               |   (IP: 10.0.0.2)      |
|---------------------|               |---------------------|
| 1. Web Server (Nginx) |               | 1. Web Server (Nginx) |
| 2. Application Server |               | 2. Application Server |
|    (App Files)        |               |    (App Files)        |
|---------------------|               |---------------------|
|       (DB Read/Write) |               |       (DB Read/Write) |
|---------------------|               |---------------------|
| ** DATABASE (MySQL) ** |<------------->| ** DATABASE (MySQL) ** |
|   (Primary/Replica    |               |   (Primary/Replica    |
|    Cluster - split    |               |    Cluster - split    |
|    across servers)    |               |    across servers)    |
+---------------------+               +---------------------+
`